records.Name: AppVenture TDX 2018
records.Description__c:
How does a bastard, orphan, unless… UNLESS! He’s been kicking ass as the ambassador to France. For once in your life, take a stand with pride. You haven’t met him yet, you haven’t had the chance. Ten-dollar founding father, You’ll blow us all away.


Everything is legal in New Jersey. How do you write like tomorrow won’t arrive? I’m not throwing away my shot! Jefferson has my vote. You will never be satisfied. The code word is ‘Rochambeau’ dig me? I was aiming for the sky.

Unless… UNLESS! When you came into the world you cried, and it broke my heart. You are the worst, Burr. I may not live to see our glory, but I will gladly join the fight. You have no control: who lives, who dies, who tells your story. Do whatever you want, I’m super dead.


Look around, look around, History has its eyes on you. Washington can’t help you now, no more Mister Nice President. Look around, look around, (He says in parentheses)


Martha Washington named her feral tomcat after him. (That's true!) Is he in Jersey? I’m just sayin’, if you really loved me, you would share him. Do you have to live an ocean away? When you came into the world you cried, and it broke my heart.


No one else was in the room where it happened. You will never be satisfied. Can I be real a second? For just a millisecond? Washington can’t help you now, no more Mister Nice President. Lord, show me how to say no to this. It's hard to listen to you with a straight face. I wrote my way out of hell, I wrote my way to revolution.


Awesome. Wow. Go home, Alexander. That’s an order from your commander. I swear your pride will be the death of us all.


For once in your life, take a stand with pride. My dog speaks more eloquently than thee. Ten-dollar founding father, You changed the melody every time. Somebody gimme some dirt on this vacuous mass so we can at last unmask him. I was aiming for the sky. Oh, let me be a part of the narrative.
